                    p.title MEIYUME transforms its manufacturing facilities to support medical staff and facilities amidst COVID-19
                    p.content Meiyume (a Fung Group company), a one-stop shop partner providing product and retail solutions for the beauty industry, is doing its part to support those impacted by the global COVID-19 pandemic.
